</head>
<body>

<a href='/users/new'> Make new user</a>
<a href='/products/new'> Make new product</a>
<a href='/products'> Browse Products for Sale</a>
    <h1><%= user.username%>'s' Page</h1>
Personal Info:<br>
<%= user.name%><br>
<%= user.email%><br>
<%= user.address%><br><br>

Products:<br> <%= user.products%><br>
